---
version: 1
op: value.score
description: is this candidate load-bearing for the query? Y/N + 1-line why
max_output_tokens: 60
vars: [query, candidate]
---
Decide if the candidate is LOAD-BEARING for the query — i.e., its presence meaningfully changes what answer the coder should give.

Query: {{.query}}
Candidate: {{.candidate}}

Output ONLY a JSON object — no prose, no markdown fence:
{"load_bearing": true|false, "confidence": 0.0-1.0, "why": "≤10 words"}

Examples:
{"load_bearing":true,"confidence":0.9,"why":"directly answers the question"}
{"load_bearing":false,"confidence":0.7,"why":"covers a different topic"}
